(589, '2026-04-08', 'Day Shift', 17, 'Redsky Morning Shift Report\n\nStation F0.board = Many NG timeouts, CIM card, top-up ng. Retested, but still ng.\n\nF0.5 WIFI = Device 615621 experienced ng at 08:23, capturing signal and ng with low value. The solution was to replace the t-pup and the woken cable.\n\nF1. RF OTA = Top-up ng WiFi TX, ZWave TX power, ZigBee TX power, and WiFi frequency. Some of the items and device 615624 had many ng ZWave TX power. The solution was to re-verify the value, then try the online test and it passed.', 62, '2026-04-08 08:20:02'),
