(598, '2026-04-08', 'Day Shift', 41, 'LINE TIDAK TARGET/UPH TIDAK TARGET\n-1.STATION RADIO BOARD HAVE 11 MACHINES\nALL MACHINES STOP RUNNING BECAUSE RF PN:69BK41D10B01 WAITING DIP FROM 08:18-08:40  ,09:30-10:14  ,14:35-14:50(PM)\n- 2 MACHINES CANT USE BECAUSE NG BDFI13 FROM 08:30-09:20 (FIXTURE)\n\n-3.STATION LED CHECK HAVE 6 MACHINES\n-1 MACHINE UNSTABLE BECAUSE NG BDFT01 FROM 07:20-09:50(FIXTURE)\n-1 MACHINE CANT USE BECAUSE NG BDFI02 FROM 08:15-08:45(FIXTURE)\n-1 MACHINE CANT USE BECAUSE NG BDFT01 FROM 10:00-11:32(FIXTURE)\n-1 MACHINE UNSTABLE BECAUSE NG BDFT01 FROM 14:20-14:50(FIXTURE)', 235, '2026-04-08 11:06:01'),
